-- Sappi Says Fine Paper, Kraft Units to Combine Operations in South Africa
-- Vernon Wessels
-- 2010-07-15T12:57:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-15/sappi-says-fine-paper-kraft-units-to-combine-operations-in-south-africa.html

          
          
             Sappi Ltd. said it was combining its
Sappi Fine Paper South Africa and Sappi Kraft businesses and
will rename the new unit Sappi Paper and Paper Packaging South
Africa, which will be headed by Jan Labuschange, the Chief
Executive Officer of its southern Africa business.  
 The Johannesburg-based company commented in an e-mailed
statement today.  
          
          


  


        